# Pages Collection and Relative Helper

## Relative
Relative helper outside of the "each pages" block.

``` html
\{{relative page assets}}
```

## Each Pages

``` html
{{#each pages}}
From **../page.dest**, to: **this.dest**: {{relative ../page.dest this.dest}}
{{/each}}
```
``` html
{{#each pages}}
From **../page.dest**, to: **assets**: {{relative ../page.dest assets}}
{{/each}}
```
``` html
{{#each pages}}
From **../page.dest**, to: **"output/assets"**: {{relative ../page.dest 'output/assets'}}
{{/each}}
```
``` html
{{#each pages}}
From **../page.dest**, to: **"src/content"**: {{relative ../page.dest 'src/content'}}
{{/each}}
```
